<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<odoo>
	<template id="portal_cadastro" name="Cadastro">
		<t t-call="bthinker_qrdoor.portal_layout">
			<t t-set="timestamp" t-value="int(time.time())"/>
			<t t-set="portal_head">
				<script t-att-src="'/bthinker_qrdoor/static/src/js/portal-cadastro.js?key={}'.format(timestamp)"/>
				<link t-att-href="'/bthinker_qrdoor/static/src/css/portal-cadastro.css?key={}'.format(timestamp)" rel="stylesheet"/>
			</t>
			<t t-set="body_class" t-value="'bg-white-200'"/>
			<t t-set="portal_body">

				<t t-if="errno == 1">
					<p><t t-esc="message"/></p>
				</t>
				<t t-else="">
					<div class="container">
						<h3 class="centered">Nova conta de Usuário</h3>
						<form id="form" method="post">
							<div id="row_fields" class="row">
								<div class="twelve columns">
									<label for="username">Nome de Usuário</label>
									<input class="twelve columns" type="text" id="username" placeholder="username" required="1"/>

									<label for="nome">Nome Completo</label>
									<input class="twelve columns" type="text" id="nome" placeholder="José da Silva" required="1"/>

									<label for="email">E-Mail</label>
									<input class="twelve columns" type="email" id="email" placeholder="exemplo@exemplo.com.br" required="1"/>

									<label for="celular">Celular</label>
									<input class="twelve columns" type="text" id="celular" placeholder="(31) 98765-4321" required="1"/>

									<label for="senha">Senha</label>
									<input class="twelve columns" type="password" id="senha" required="1"/>

									<label for="confirma_senha">Confirmação de Senha</label>
									<input class="twelve columns" type="password" id="confirma_senha" required="1"/>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div id="row_termos" class="row">
								<label>Termos de uso:</label>
								<div class="twelve columns">
									<span>Estou ciente de que prosseguindo com este cadastro, autorizo a B-Thinker a armazenar e utilizar meus dados pessoais aqui fornecidos para os fins aos quais este sistema se destina.</span>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div id="row_checkbox" class="row">
								<div class="twelve columns">
									<input type="checkbox" id="termo"/>
									<span>Concordo com os termos de uso</span>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div id="row_save_button" class="twelve columns centered">
								<button type="button" class="button-primary" id="btn_save">Registrar</button>
							</div>
						</form>
					</div>
				</t>
			</t>
		</t>
	</template>
</odoo>
